{"tid":126924,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"香港飲食革命 - yelp","createTime":"2017-02-19T17:14:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-20T18:51:45.000Z","uid":68568,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7b041a01889ecc301ee35217431567040987ab34","tid":126924,"uid":68568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:14:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/20/010319_247e847e63d8693872748f80d9181ff3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F20%2F010319_247e847e63d8693872748f80d9181ff3.jpg&h=0f73eeaf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>咩係yelp?</strong><br />\nyelp係一個2004年成立嘅網站，提供本地嘅餐飲資訊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>點解要用yelp?</strong><br />\n現有嘅飲食資訊平台質素不堪入目，大多都係接受商家嘅利益後發出，未能夠反映餐廳嘅真實狀況，某啲平台又容許商家刪除負評，令一眾市民唔能夠有效咁尋找合適嘅餐廳。<br />\n而yelp 呢個平台容許用家自由發表評論，商家不能夠刪除評論，令劣鳩會唔變上菜。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>邊度下載yelp?</strong><br />\niOS: <a href=\"https://itunes.apple.com/us/developer/yelp/id284910353\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fitunes.apple.com%2Fus%2Fdeveloper%2Fyelp%2Fid284910353&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=0e91f1ff\" target=\"_blank\">https://itunes.apple.com/us/developer/yelp/id284910353</a><br />\nAndroid: <a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.yelp.android&amp;hl=en\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.yelp.android%26hl%3Den&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=e1481e1e\" target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.yelp.android&amp;hl=en</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong>我有咩要做？</strong><br />\n下載yelp到你嘅電話，上載食評。<br />\n依家yelp hk 嘅資料庫仲未完善，有好多餐廳都未登記，亦有唔少無相，希望各位有心嘅巴絲可以幫手完善資料庫。<br />\n登記餐廳：<a href=\"https://en.biz.yelp.com.hk/signup_business/new?country=HK&amp;context=1FRrsc4UgcYmdiomKG2zZQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.biz.yelp.com.hk%2Fsignup_business%2Fnew%3Fcountry%3DHK%26context%3D1FRrsc4UgcYmdiomKG2zZQ&d=O1gn%2BLisHAK1lZrgQK9vXJZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=538b5715\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.biz.yelp.com.hk/signup_business/new?country=HK&amp;context=1FRrsc4UgcYmdiomKG2zZQ</a><br />\n上載相可以到個app 入面完成。<br />\n希望各位巴絲可以將屋企，公司，學校附近嘅餐廳嘅資料都入到個app 入面。<br />\n另外就要多啲鼓勵親朋戚友用yelp 。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>希望可以集眾巴絲之力，抗衡____男女，新____，開__喇等良莠不齊嘅飲食資訊平台。</strong>"},{"pid":"6515ae26cb9ba9579dc1ce82517af3bec5943c51","tid":126924,"uid":68568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:17:23.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"bcd08e6094f71b12c31af94a12a332a850718061","tid":126924,"uid":68568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:24:45.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"2f5b21a7352d867946d6adb05722801b095f9df1","tid":126924,"uid":68568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:24:58.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"8976a3e51fdad34ab316edf18268434d12d2cb2d","tid":126924,"uid":68568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:25:11.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"76a2b6ac585a29057d06e572fc88cdb367a7394c","tid":126924,"uid":4346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:27:38.000Z","msg":"你係網主?"},{"pid":"645833e489899daa845b1008d661be26aa0ded36","tid":126924,"uid":36509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:31:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你係網主?</blockquote><br />\nyelp外國好出名<br />\n係香港人用開openrice姐"},{"pid":"a925dcd51a76caa2c60cc548bf5559b05a2220c5","tid":126924,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:32:17.000Z","msg":"點保證比你地做大之後唔會又係一撚樣<br />\n<br />\n仲比你地賺埋錢<br />\n<br />\n麻煩好似google 咁透明先好出黎屌其他人<br />\n<br />\n例如你有獨立知名人士/有公開透明既制度/你自己諗，乜都冇叫人支持就等收皮"},{"pid":"05787997ed82df3196e6dcfe63ba8be70c68d29a","tid":126924,"uid":771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-19T17:33:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點保證比你地做大之後唔會又係一撚樣<br />\n<br />\n仲比你地賺埋錢<br 